## dev-ai-tools version

Read the `VERSION` file in the `search.tool.dev-ai-tools` repo root for the current version.

## Plain ASCII text

Use plain ASCII characters instead of Unicode equivalents unless Unicode is genuinely required (e.g. a proper noun, a language that needs it, or a symbol with no ASCII equivalent).

- Use `--` instead of the em dash or en dash Unicode characters
- Use `"` and `'` instead of curly/smart quote Unicode characters
- Use `...` instead of the ellipsis Unicode character
